com.petpet.c3po.api.model
Interface Model

All Known Implementing Classes:
ActionLog, Element, Property, Source
public interface Model

An empty interface that designates the classes that have to be supported by a PersistenceLayer provider. It is also used to restrict passing other objects to the persistence layer at compile time.

Petar Petrov
